Immediate Vacancy Camp Boss Premier Job in Dubai
Posted: 7 days ago
Immediate Vacancy Camp Boss Premier Composite Technologies (PCT) is a global supplier and manufacturer of large scale, advanced, high quality, epoxy composite components. We seek a competent Camp Boss to manage our labour camp of 900 residents, based in DIP, Dubai. Suitable candidate will be on bachelor status, and live in the labour camp (own room). He will be responsible for both facilities maintenance and monitoring the overall activities of our camp residents. He will have 5+ years previous experience in a similar role. Suitable candidate will possess the additional following qualities: 1. Excellent communication skills (Spoken English essential). 2. Ability to assert authority in a calm and constructive manner. 3. Level-headed / able to assess situations from all angles. 4. Computer literate (good working knowledge of Microsoft Office). Please send applications by
